<li><a href="/index.php/Chromium" title="Chromium">Chromium</a></li>
<li><a href="/index.php/Opera" title="Opera">Opera</a></li>
</ul></div>
<p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.mozilla.org/firefox">Firefox</a> is a popular open source graphical web browser from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.mozilla.org">Mozilla</a>.
</p>
